data.description: This 2300 sq ft townhouse offers a unique opportunity to have spaciousness, but a small yard for those who want less maintenance. The main floor has a master bedroom with its own bath, plus an additional bedroom and full bathroom.  The beautiful hardwood floors and lots of extra storage add the perfect touch.  Down in the basement you will find a large open family room with built-ins for abundant storage, another bedroom and bath, plus a utility room & another room for crafts or office space.  Recent LVP flooring throughout lower level. There is lots of flexible space for all your needs, that's for sure.  The 2-car garage has one side with a taller garage door so you can park your truck.  And the private backyard has plenty of room on the deck for a barbecue and a place to relax and dine, but it's set up with not much yardwork.  Add a couple containers with flowers and you're set for the summer.  It sits among a neighborhood of newer nicely landscaped homes close to shopping and restaurants you can walk to.
